Sentencas: Nd0.6Sr0.4Fe0.96Zn0.04O3-delta showed the highest conductivity of 108.78 S cm(-1) at 700 degrees C. EIS indicated that an appropriate amount of Zn doping can improve the oxygen transport capacity.

Sentencas: A single cell with Nd0.6Sr0.4Fe0.96Zn0.04O3-delta as the cathode showed a peak power density of 306.37 mW cm(-2) at 800 degrees C, proving that the introduction of an appropriate amount of Zn can improve the electrochemical performance of a material.
